The screen also indicates that logging out will deactivate all Secret Chats.

flow_desc: The flow for signing out of an account begins with the user tapping the menu icon on the app's interface. Next, they navigate to the settings by selecting the settings text view. Once in the settings, they find the three vertical dots icon and tap it. This leads them to their profile, where they select the Log Out option. The user then confirms their intention to log out by tapping the Log Out button at the bottom of the screen, which prompts a confirmation message. Finally, they confirm logging out, acknowledging that all Secret Chats will be canceled.
